abstract: President Trump has signaled displeasure with the American ally. His lawyer has been pressing the government in Kiev to investigate his political foes.
snippet: President Trump has signaled displeasure with the American ally. His lawyer has been pressing the government in Kiev to investigate his political foes.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON â€” The White House delayed a package of military assistance to the new government in Ukraine, and has yet to schedule a White House meeting for its new president. After abruptly pulling the previous American ambassador out of Kiev when conservatives questioned her political loyalty, President Trump has yet to nominate a successor.

lead_paragraph: MANCHESTER, N.H. â€” Joseph R. Biden Jr.â€™s backers roared supportive slogans and banged on drums as they awaited his arrival outside Southern New Hampshire University Arena. Senator Bernie Sanders was welcomed by die-hard fans ready to cheer seemingly every sentence he uttered. Mayor Pete Buttigieg and Senator Cory Booker delivered one applause line after the next.

abstract: Mr. Schultz said he had concluded that an independent bid would pose too great a risk of helping President Trump win a second term.
snippet: Mr. Schultz said he had concluded that an independent bid would pose too great a risk of helping President Trump win a second term.
lead_paragraph: Howard Schultz, the former chief executive of Starbucks who took steps earlier this year to prepare to run for president as an independent, announced Friday that he was abandoning those plans.
